title: South Park S12E07 - Super Fun Time
description:
Mr. Garrison takes the fourth grade class on an educational field trip to a Pioneer Village where dedicated workers remain in character as their counterparts from the 1800&#039;s. Cartman forces Butters to ditch the fanatical townsfolk to go to the amusement center located next door. While the rest of kids are reluctantly learning about the good old days in Colorado, a group of trigger-happy thieves break into the museum and take everyone hostage.



"Just to let you know. THIS IS THE LAST EPISODE FOR THIS BATCH, IT WILL BE ABOUT 5 MONTHS BEFORE THE SEASON CONTINUES"
